  "detailed_description": "<br><br>\"Asa-Chan Wants to Go Home!\" is an RPG game produced by プラスカゼット and published by Hanabi games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646240/extras/6ae3f7ce2a75eab2cef53f9e5cf028e0.avif?t=1738628978\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><br>This is a small adventure story... Asanuma Sayaka is an ordinary girl, but one day, she is suddenly transported to another world and becomes a hero. Here, she faces a tremendous challenge...<br><br>Players will control the main character, Asanuma Sayaka, to challenge the legendary \"Disaster Witch\". Along the way, she will encounter obstacles from demons, but there's also a chance to get along well with them...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646240/extras/47e6bba4a7cf374d38ffe451ee3d8363.avif?t=1738628978\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646240/extras/71ad502ccee00da098c276e70842c0f0.avif?t=1738628978\" width=550 height=380 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646240/extras/7b6bd2ffac8b9a842c6cddd96d619881.avif?t=1738628978\" width=550 height=380 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646240/extras/39fbe628e2b148d8531d7a7318332bdf.avif?t=1738628978\" width=550 height=70 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Jrpg<br></li><li>Captivating story</li></ul>",
